[2026-05-19T02:04:19.177Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"065af8078fc62c1e15e59836ec517a8f","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_function_l1xsbtz761bj_1","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/education/META.md","old_string":"# META — Education Screen Design\n\n## Example Selection\n\n| Criterion | Weight | Browse Screen | Library Screen | Health-log Screen |\n|-----------|--------|---------------|----------------|-------------------|\n| Topic list with icons | Required | ✓ (category chips) | ✓ (bookshelf grid) | ✓ (symptom list) |\n| Scrollable content | Required | ✓ (vertical scroll) | ✓ (vertical scroll) | ✓ (vertical scroll) |\n| Card-based layout | Required | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n| AppBar with actions | Required | ✓ (search icon) | ✓ (filter icon) | ✓ (back + actions) |\n| Push route (hidden bottom nav) | Required | N/A | N/A | ✓ |\n| Featured/hero section | Helpful | ✓ (promotional banner) | ✓ (featured book) | Partial |\n| Horizontal scrolling list | Helpful | ✓ (trending) | ✓ (continue reading) | ✓ (quick logs) |\n| Grid layout for categories | Helpful | ✓ (2-col categories) | ✓ (bookshelf grid) | Partial |\n| Search functionality | Required | ✓ | ✓ | Partial |\n| **Total Score** | | **9** | **9** | **8** |\n\n## Selected Reference: Browse Screen\n\nThe Browse screen (`/browse`) provides the best template for the Education screen:\n- Similar push route structure with hidden BottomNavigationBar\n- Grid of topic/category cards as primary navigation\n- Horizontal scrolling \"Recent\" list\n- Search in AppBar\n- Card-based content with images and badges\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n1. **No SliverAppBar collapse** — Education uses a static AppBar with search icon, similar to Health-log\n2. **2-column topic grid** — Mirrors Browse's category grid, 5 topics fit well in 2×3 (with one empty)\n3. **Horizontal recent articles list** — Follows Browse's trending section pattern\n4. **Featured article hero** — Uses the promotional banner pattern from Browse\n5. **Search overlay** — Bottom sheet approach consistent with the app's modal pattern\n\n## Reference Screen Pattern\n\n```\nBrowseScreen → EducationScreen\n├── Scaffold with CustomScrollView\n├── AppBar: \"Browse\"/\"Education\", back button, search icon\n├── Featured content card at top\n├── 2-column category/topic grid\n├── Horizontal scrolling recent/trending list\n└── BottomNavigationBar (hidden on push)\n```\n\n## Flutter HTML Glossary Elements Used\n\n- `.scaffold` — Main scaffold wrapper\n- `.app-bar` — App bar with title and actions\n- `.card` — Article and topic cards\n- `.chip` — Topic badges and filter chips\n- `.row` / `.column` — Layout containers\n- `.network-image` / `.placeholder-image` — Article illustrations\n- `data-color` — Color scheme roles\n- `data-spacing` — Spacing tokens\n- `data-route` — Navigation routes","new_string":"# META — Education Screen Design\n\n## Example Selection\n\n| Criterion | Weight | single-screen.html (Home) | multi-state-screen.html (Mood) | celebration-screen.html (Pregnancy) |\n|-----------|--------|----------------------------|-------------------------------|-----------------------------------|\n| App Type | High | ✓ Pregnancy Tracker | ✓ Pregnancy Tracker | ✓ Pregnancy Tracker |\n| Platform | High | ✓ Phone 375px | ✓ Phone 375px | ✓ Phone 375px |\n| Interaction Density | Medium | ✓ Medium (browse/tap) | ✗ High (forms/charts) | ✗ Medium (celebration) |\n| Visual Personality | Medium | ✓ Card-based, warm pastel | ✓ Card-based, warm | ✓ Card-based, warm |\n| Component Overlap | Medium | ✓ Hero + grid + horiz-scroll | ✓ Cards, charts | ✓ Hero + cards |\n| Screen Pattern Match | High | ✓ Single Screen | ✗ Multi-State | ✗ Celebration |\n| **Total Score** | | **30/30** Strong Match | **18/30** Moderate | **18/30** Moderate |\n\n## Selected Reference: single-screen.html (Home)\n\n**Strong Match** — Used as structural base for Education screen.\n\n### Why single-screen.html?\n\n1. **App Type Match**: Both pregnancy tracker apps; Education is a content discovery hub like Home is a health tracking hub\n2. **Screen Pattern Match**: Single-screen with hero section + grid + horizontal scroll — identical structure to Education\n3. **Component Overlap**: Featured card (≈week-banner), topic grid (≈quick-actions), recent articles (≈checklist-chips)\n4. **Interaction Density**: Both medium — browsing, tapping, scrolling (not complex forms/multi-state)\n5. **Visual Personality**: Same design system (Gentle Bloom), same Nunito font, same card-based aesthetic\n\n### Adaptations Applied\n\n| Original (Home) | Education Screen |\n|-----------------|------------------|\n| AppBar (title + avatar) | AppBar (title + back btn + search icon) |\n| Week banner hero | Featured article hero card |\n| 2×2 quick-actions grid | 2-column topic grid (5 items) |\n| Horizontal checklist chips | Horizontal recent article cards |\n| Bottom nav (visible) | Bottom nav hidden (push route) |\n| No search overlay | Search icon triggers bottom sheet |\n\n## Flutter HTML Glossary Elements Used\n\n- `data-flutter=\"scaffold\"` — Main scaffold wrapper\n- `data-flutter=\"app-bar\"` — App bar with title and actions\n- `data-flutter=\"card\"` — Article and topic cards\n- `data-flutter=\"chip\"` — Topic badges and filter chips\n- `data-flutter=\"grid\"` — Topic grid layout\n- `data-flutter=\"horizontal-scroll\"` — Recent articles list\n- `data-color` — Color scheme roles (primary, secondary, tertiary)\n- `data-route` — Navigation routes\n- `class=\"scaffold\"` — Flutter HTML Glossary scaffold class marker"}}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":51060,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":23245},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e7ed62d8-d4ad-4b52-b05e-5c7ae456d331","uu