- `.chip` — Topic badges and filter chips
- `.row` / `.column` — Layout containers
- `.network-image` / `.placeholder-image` — Article illustrations
- `data-color` — Color scheme roles
- `data-spacing` — Spacing tokens
- `data-route` — Navigation routes
